-Teltoli-

She walks in a little more, and comes to the War Room. She sees it empty, and she sighs. This was boring! There was never ANY action with the Maximals! And Liono Prime was never around!

"Boring!" She says to herself, loud enough for any bot to hear her that was near. 

Deciding what to do, she wanders into the control room and stares at all the stuff, far too complicated for her to even think about. She laughs, remembering what she would have done when she was little.. 'Ooohh, what does THIS button do?'.
